    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this fast-paced, infinite jumping adventure, guide your cat as they leap from platform to platform, racing against the rising water that speeds up the longer you survive. Precision and quick reflexes are key as you collect milk and fish for bonus points, all while navigating randomly generated platforms. With its charming pixel art and simple controls, the game offers a challenging yet rewarding experience where every jump counts. A throwback to simpler times. How high can you climb before the water catches up?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Randomly generated platforms keep every run fresh and unpredictable.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The water rises <i>faster</i> and <i>faster</i> every few seconds, adding to the challenge.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Simple yet responsive controls, perfect for quick sessions or extended play.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect milk for points and fish for even more bonus points.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Charming pixel art style, evoking the nostalgia of classic games.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock Steam achievements as you master the game.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Steam Deck, Linux, and Windows support.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports many controllers with plug-and-play functionality.</p></li></ul>",
